panels.description: This measurement provides the number of RRC connection establishment attempts for each establishment cause.

targets.query:
from(bucket: "rrc_connection_metrics")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    (r._measurement == "RRCConnEstabAtt") and
    r._field == "Value" and
    (
      "${NetworkFunctionId}" == "All" or r.NetworkFunctionId == "${NetworkFunctionId}" or contains(value: r.NetworkFunctionId, set: ${NetworkFunctionId:json})
    )
  )
  |> group(columns: ["NetworkFunctionId"])
  |> pivot(rowKey: ["_time"], columnKey: ["_measurement"], valueColumn: "_value")
    |> map(fn: (r) => ({
      _time: r._time,
      NetworkFunctionId:r.NetworkFunctionId,
      "Id": r.RRCConnEstabAtt
  }))
  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "Id", "NetworkFunctionId"])

panels.title: RRC Connection Attempts

targets.query:
from(bucket: "rrc_connection_metrics")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    (r._measurement == "RRCConnEstabSucc" or r._measurement == "RRCConnEstabAtt") and
    (
      "${NetworkFunctionId}" == "All" or r.NetworkFunctionId == "${NetworkFunctionId}" or contains(value: r.NetworkFunctionId, set: ${NetworkFunctionId:json})
    )
  )
  |> group(columns: ["NetworkFunctionId", "_measurement"])
  |> sum(column: "_value")
  |> pivot(rowKey: ["NetworkFunctionId"], columnKey: ["_measurement"], valueColumn: "_value")
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({
      NetworkFunctionId: r.NetworkFunctionId,
      RRCConnSuccessRate: float(v: r.RRCConnEstabSucc ) / float(v: r.RRCConnEstabAtt) *100.0  }))
  |> group() 
  |> mean(column: "RRCConnSuccessRate")
  |> yield(name: "RRC Connection Success Rate")

targets.query:
from(bucket: "pdu_session_management_metrics")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop) 
  |> filter(fn: (r) => 
    r._measurement == "SMPDUSessionSetupFail" and
    (
      "${NetworkFunctionId}" == "All" or r.NetworkFunctionId == "${NetworkFunctionId}" or contains(value: r.NetworkFunctionId, set: ${NetworkFunctionId:json})
    )
  )
  |> group(columns: ["NrCellId", "PlmnId"])
  |> sum(column: "_value")
  |> group() 
  |> sum(column: "_value")
  |> yield(name: "Number of PDU sessions failed to setup")

panels.title: PDU Session Setup Failures

list.definition:
from(bucket: "rrc_connection_metrics")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop) 
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == "RRCConnMean") 
  |> keep(columns: ["NetworkFunctionId"]) 
  |> distinct(column: "NetworkFunctionId")
  |> sort(columns: ["NetworkFunctionId"], desc: false)
list.name: NetworkFunctionId
